and height <nobr>approx. 6-7 cm<\/nobr>) in Varoma dish. Distribute batter between them then cover each cup with heat-resistant cling film and steam <nobr><strong>40 min\/Varoma\/speed 1.<\/strong><\/nobr>","<i>No oven? No problem! Steaming produces surprisingly tender cakes, and the gentle heat allows you to melt chocolate for glazing at the same time as the cake steams. Different types of tins or bowls can be used for steaming cakes, as the temperature is lower than in an oven. Have a look at the variations to see the many ways this recipe can be adapted to your preferences.<\/i>"],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","2h 20m","12 slices"]}